data.description: Check out this stunning home located at Campanella Estates in Estacada. This 2020 new construction home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, & 2,070sqft of living space. Inside you'll find an open concept living space, high ceilings, large kitchen w/island open to the living room; perfect for entertaining. Dining area, 3 spacious guest bedrooms 2 of which are separate from primary, huge primary w/tub, full shower, his/ her sinks & large walk-in closet. Garage has costum cabinets & work bench. Fully fenced & landscaped front &  back yard w/hot-tub & sprinklers, heat pump, and more.
